 />\n點可能推返所有疑點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"608c68ad68ceaadb6e6e8ac70c54c30a05f1cdb8","tid":267490,"uid":78521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T10:52:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>L係直昇機，夜神月竟然可以係隔離寫字殺人<br />\n有冇咁底B呀？</blockquote><br />\n寫完血書成班友當無哂件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n重睇啦 佢用手錶入面張紙寫 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04605c65101006d988cc7945e05872750565c8bb","tid":267490,"uid":78521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T10:55:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>同埋L有筆記在手後，只要立即測試下筆記有無預約死亡日期，咁夜神月同海砂坐監既清白亦會被推翻，唉，作者寫到L根本係智障<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你係咪on9啊<br />\n夜神月同海砂坐監既清白係因為繼續有新聞報導既犯人比人殺<br />\n而比人監禁既夜神月同海砂冇可能有方法知道新聞有咩犯人<br />\n所以先證明到佢地清白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n只能證明權力轉移既可能<br />\n點可能推返所有疑點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所以咪叫月老豆扮殺佢地<br />\n果時L就諗佢地係奇拿就會反殺月老豆啦<br />\n但L果陣唔知道奇拿殺人係用筆記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0622620396ead1636b71702f7b434925ccc7e3eb","tid":267490,"uid":24455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T10:57:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>L係直昇機，夜神月竟然可以係隔離寫字殺人<br />\n有冇咁底B呀？</blockquote><br />\n寫完血書成班友當無哂件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n重睇啦 佢用手錶入面張紙寫 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n本筆記一到手佢成個人背住L座<br />\n跟住火口死左，仲唔係當L白癡<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf0dc4c0417098ef561f480ad44cd29c33dd37e3","tid":267490,"uid":24455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T11:00:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote